# Asset folders structure

Create these folders and add your files:

## Folder Structure:
```
/assets/
├── images/           # General images
├── photos/           # Your photo memories
├── songs/            # MP3 audio files for songs
├── voices/           # Voice note recordings
├── shayariVoice/     # Voice recordings of shayaris
├── moods/            # Images and audio for mood section
├── food/             # Food images
└── proposals/        # Proposal idea images
```

## How to add your files:
1. Clone this project to your computer
2. Create the folders listed above in `/assets/`
3. Add your audio files (.mp3) and images (.jpg, .png) to the appropriate folders
4. The app will automatically load them based on the JSON data files

## Example file names (match these in your JSON files):
- /assets/songs/our-song.mp3
- /assets/photos/first-photo.jpg
- /assets/voices/morning-message.mp3
- /assets/images/morning.jpg

All paths are already configured in the JSON data files in /src/data/
